@startuml analysis-pipeline
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam DefaultFontName Segoe UI
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #1565C0
skinparam ActivityFontColor #0D47A1
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF8E1
skinparam ArrowColor #1565C0
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #FBC02D

title <b>Data Analysis Life Cycle (DALC) - Poshtique Project</b>

start
:<b>1. Business Understanding & Data Collection</b>;
note right
  - Owner interviews with Purnima
    and Noopur Mehta
  - Receive 2024 CSV sales data
    (Summary + Details)
end note

:<b>2. Data Preprocessing</b>;
note right
  - Impute missing states & pincodes
  - Standardize customer/product names
  - Categorize products as
    Sweet vs Savory
end note

:<b>3. Geo-tagging & Location Analysis</b>;
note right
  - Excel VLOOKUP against global
    lat/long dataset
  - Build hotspot maps in Power BI
end note

:<b>4. Descriptive Analysis</b>;
note right
  - Central tendency on order values
  - Channel distribution
  - Product mix per order
end note

:<b>5. Data Modeling & Diagnostic</b>;
note right
  - Monthly product trends
  - Seasonal heatmaps
  - Sankey: Channel -> Product -> City
end note

:<b>6. Apply Analytical Frameworks</b>;
note right
  SWOT  |  Pareto  |  ABC  |  RFM
end note

:<b>7. Inventory Optimization</b>;
note right
  - Economic Order Quantity (EOQ)
  - Reorder Level (ROL)
  - Stockout impact ~ 6.26%
    of gross sales
end note

:<b>8. Interpretation of Results</b>;
:<b>9. Actionable Recommendations</b>;
stop

@enduml
